<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center bg-light p-5 rounded shadow-lg">
        <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold text-success mb-4">GRAMIN BAZZAR</h1>
        <p class="lead text-secondary fs-5">
            Gramin Bazzar is an <strong>e-commerce platform</strong> designed to empower rural communities in Nepal
            by connecting <strong>local producers, farmers, and artisans</strong> directly with consumers.
        </p>
